definitions.definition: A usually abundant, luxuriant growth over or on something else.

subdefinitions.definition: A tangle of growth occurring at the top of trees involving vines and branches, common in jungles.

definitions.definition: An excessive growth or increase in numbers, as in a population of weeds or microbes .
Excessive size; usually caused by over-production of growth hormone from the pituitary gland .
